Trade/Device Name(s): FreeStyle Precision Neo H Blood Glucose Monitoring System
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): FreeStyle Precision Neo H Blood Glucose Test Strips
FreeStyle Auto-Assist Neo Data Management System
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for FreeStyle Precision Neo H Blood Glucose Monitoring System for quantitative measurement of glucose in whole blood using amperometric technology
Indications for Use Summary: Intended for quantitative measurement of glucose in fresh capillary whole blood from the finger, and venous and arterial whole blood, for multiple-patient use in professional healthcare settings as an aid to monitor the effectiveness of a diabetes control program; not for diagnosis or screening for diabetes or neonatal testing
